43:14.625 --> 43:17.208
Jack, you still in there?

43:36.125 --> 43:37.583
(ROARS)

43:47.541 --> 43:48.875
(GASPING SOFTLY)

43:58.166 --> 44:00.375
-(SNARLS SOFTLY)
-(SHUDDERING)

44:30.166 --> 44:31.791
(SHUDDERS)

44:40.833 --> 44:45.166
Elsa! You let him go!

44:50.333 --> 44:54.208
You will now die, as you lived,

44:54.791 --> 44:58.166
a disgrace to your father's memory,

44:59.333 --> 45:02.166
and the hallowed Bloodstone name!

45:02.250 --> 45:03.375
