45:04.583 --> 45:06.083
(GASPING)

45:06.750 --> 45:08.083
(SCREAMING)

45:18.875 --> 45:20.458
(TED ROARS SOFTLY)

45:25.708 --> 45:27.458
He went that way.

45:27.583 --> 45:29.541
(GROWLS SOFTLY)

45:43.541 --> 45:44.916
There you are, mistress.

45:46.708 --> 45:52.333
I only wanted to
make myself available to you.

45:53.166 --> 45:55.916
Brilliant. You can start
clearing all this shit up.

