-(GROWLS SOFTLY)
-Oh, yeah, thanks, Ted.

47:01.333 --> 47:02.333
Thanks, man.

47:13.375 --> 47:14.416
Is she okay?

47:14.791 --> 47:16.041
(GROWLS SOFTLY)

47:17.416 --> 47:18.958
Good. That's good.

47:20.333 --> 47:21.541
(GROWLS SOFTLY)

47:25.708 --> 47:26.791
(LAUGHS)

47:34.166 --> 47:36.041
What? No.

47:37.375 --> 47:41.166
No, I'm the one who comes to your rescue.
What are you talkin' about?

47:41.750 --> 47:43.041
Whatever. No.

47:45.208 --> 47:46.416
(GROWLS SOFTLY)

47:46.500 --> 47:49.083
Man, I cannot think of food
right now. I'm...

47:51.500 --> 47:55.666
Let's do sushi. I owe you that. Yes.

